longBusinessSummary: EQL Pharma AB (publ) engages in the development, marketing, and sale of generic medicines to pharmacies and hospitals in Sweden, Denmark, Norway, Finland, and the rest of Europe. It offers injection products for inpatient care and formulations for outpatient care. EQL Pharma AB (publ) was incorporated in 2006 and is based in Lund, Sweden.
